  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16592</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20831</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>食人魔的脚步让房子也在震动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20831</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23884</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>脚步声越来越大。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23884</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28331</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>食人魔的妻子看起来很担心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28331</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39113</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快！”她小声对杰克说，“躲起来！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39113</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48954</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>像上次一样，杰克躲进了烤箱里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48954</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51256</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>咚！咚！咚！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51256</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55241</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>食人魔走进房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55241</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63084</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他又开始用鼻子闻来闻去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63084</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71076</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“Fee！Fi！Fo！Fum！”食人魔大喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71076</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73560</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我闻到一个......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73560</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78742</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没什么味道，亲爱的！”妻子急忙说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78742</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82763</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“来，吃早饭吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82763</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88894</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妻子把煎饼放在桌子上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88894</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92925</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧！”食人魔生气地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92925</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96409</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可是我真的闻到......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96409</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101316</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妻子急忙在煎饼上撒了一些蓝莓。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101316</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104433</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>食人魔开心地看着煎饼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104433</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117774</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇！是我最爱的蓝莓！”他大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117774</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130156</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克看着食人魔大口地吃着煎饼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130156</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>吃完早饭，食人魔拍了拍肚子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135054</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后他突然拍了拍桌子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142596</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“老婆！”他大喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142596</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146033</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把我的金母鸡抱来！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146034</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152465</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妻子点了点头，跑了出去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152465</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156678</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，她抱着一只金母鸡回来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156678</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161713</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把金母鸡放在食人魔面前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161713</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166336</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>食人魔邪恶地笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166336</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173491</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“母鸡呀，我要一个鸡蛋！”食人魔大喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173491</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195480</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快下蛋！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195480</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198204</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克睁大了眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198204</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204605</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>母鸡下了一个金蛋！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204605</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209737</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我一定要带走那只母鸡！”杰克心想。</Text>
